response.overview: "Frank Carson - Live (1993)" is a riotous comedy show featuring the legendary Irish comedian Frank Carson. In this uproarious performance, Carson delivers an evening of non-stop laughter, wit, and classic humor. With his infectious energy and trademark catchphrases, he regales the audience with a mix of uproarious one-liners, hilarious anecdotes, and playful banter that spans a wide range of topics, from family life to everyday absurdities. Join Frank Carson for an unforgettable night of timeless comedy that showcases his unmatched talent for entertaining and leaving audiences in stitches.
response.title: Frank Carson: Live
